{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got a-- you know, we still-- the war still going on, and goddamn, I want to get back into-- into combat and do some more shooting up and blah, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just crazy talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these guys picked up on it right away, too, because they knew, you know, coming from me and Snyder, the other guy that-- from our squadron, from our squadron that was with me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a drinker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he wasn't flying, he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean drunk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Asleep drunk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he was flying, he was cool and good, but when he wasn't flying, when he was back at the-- at-- at Frankfurt, he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't have-- you could have stuck him in a tub of hot water and he wouldn't have known it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He wouldn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But-- but he told some of the, you know, the guys, you guys wouldn't believe us if we told you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were a couple of days I took my flight suit that I had on at-- at Dachau, and I had a pair of $50 Wellington boots, handmade for me in London-- and these were-- these were ego trip fighter pilot boots-- and my flight-- my pinks and my flight suit and my jacket, that I have a picture over there-- but that's a different one.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, the, you know, trousers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have-- OD-- it's just, uh, OD pants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're a little bit on the pink side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called them pinks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had grays and pinks and ODs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for some reason I had a pair of pinks on at some point in time in this thing, which were the ones that were-- that I thought smelled so bad.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
